All users of the Clinic Management System agree to:

1. Use the software responsibly.
2. Maintain the confidentiality of login credentials.
3. Prevent unauthorized access to patient information.
4. Comply with applicable healthcare and privacy regulations.
5. Avoid misuse of system resources.
6. Report security vulnerabilities when discovered.
7. Ensure the accuracy of entered data.

Failure to comply with these responsibilities may result in termination of access privileges.

